.Dd $Mdocdate: September 23 2023 $
.Dt STFRNG 4 riscv64
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm stfrng
.Nd StarFive JH7110 random number generator
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "stfrng* at fdt?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the random number generator found on the
StarFive JH7110 SoC.
.Pp
It feeds the random subsystem's entropy pool with 256 bits of random
data every second.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr random 4 ,
.Xr arc4random 9
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 7.4 .
.Sh AUTHORS
.An -nosplit
